name: Jenny
description: Tiny, fierce, adorable. Wickedly smart. Not a fan of strangers but very social once she knows you.

name: Emma
quirk: She loves to roll onto her head until she flips over waiting for a belly rub.
does_best: Emma is the best at snuggling up into a tight ball so she can sleep on my lap (she is not a small dog at all!)
fun_story: Emma loves to hunt for birds, frogs and turtles. One day I was out with her at her favorite swimming spot. She ran right into the bushes and came back out to me with a bird in her mouth! She was so proud of herself as she pranced around with her prize. This was her first bird!

name: Tod
description: A very proud papillon and legs-crossed lap-seeker. Tod can jump to very high ledges, a skill we suspect he learned from our cats.
ancestry_info: Purebred Papillon, parents registered with AKC

name: Rosie
description: A very sweet and attention-seeking (perhaps mixed) papillon girl. Her ears were so big as a pup that she could barely hold them up.
ancestry_info: Not confidently purebred, parents were not registered with AKC but rather some other dog club.

name: Benny
description: Benny was born to race in Florida. He was very successful, and only recently stopped racing in March 2020. He gets very excited when in a new environment or when meeting new people, trying to nibble on them. He has a cropped tail due to "Happy Tail" injuries.

name: Shadow
description: Shadow is a pretty energetic and sweet dog.  He's also super smart!
